* Maven2

We use maven2 to manage project. To compile and run unit tests, install maven
and run 'mvn compile' 

* Log Levels
Let's use the level:
  - SEVERE (for fatal errors);
  - WARNING (for other errors);
  - INFO (for high level trace/debug messages - use with caution - startup/essential methods);
  - FINE (for low level trace/debug messages - for most traces).
Other log recommendations:
  - Avoid anonymous logger, instead use ClassName.class.getName();
  - Name the Logger object as "logger".
  - To log Errors/Exceptions use: logger.log(Level.(WARNING|SEVERE),message, throwable);
